Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.75,0:24:50.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inherited desires. Tested bonds.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.25,0:24:52.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next time, "Season of Awakening."
